  <main>
    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/part-i/article-xiii/section-1301"
             temporalId="sSection 1301">
      <num>Section 1301</num>
      <heading>Special municipal elections</heading>
      <content>
        <p>All other municipal elections that may be held by authority of this Charter, or of
               general law, or by ordinance, shall be known as special municipal elections.</p>
      </content>
    </section>
